01:13:15.000 --> 01:13:30.000
But anyway Dr. King came over and I remember his telling the people and he has used this terminology or had used it more than once but he said to the to the now about to be graduates of our citizenship education workshop.

01:13:30.000 --> 01:13:59.000
Nobody can ride your back if your backs not bent a metaphor I hope people will get that as they see my book but I decided that was what we were doing at the woman who was complaining that the city clerk treated her so badly you know you can be feel sorry for yourself or what was been the rest of your life angry or you can become the city clerk and nobody can ride your back if your backs not bent and the subtitle the movement from victim to victory.

