01:14:30.000 --> 01:14:59.000
We had a training workshop which we held every convened every month and and then other people would come and it was very it was very powerful the experience and had I remember once you know singing was so important in the civil rights movement and I remember I love to sing even though I you know I don't read a note of music people ask me what key do you want to do.

